{"about_the_game":"Light Odyssey is a boss rush/soul-like action game in which you have to take down a series of colossus carrying the source of light.<br><br>You find yourself at the end of the world, led by the dying light. You will be asked to engage in a fierce battle against giant enemies, made more enjoyable by one-of-a-kind graphic design inspired by light and darkness, and a quick battle system. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902860/extras/2024-09-17_14-29-08.gif?t=1736492231\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Taking Down the Colossus</strong></h2>There are giant enemies carrying mystic powers throughout the world of Light Odyssey. Each with its own unique strength, these powerful colossi will not hesitate to take you down. Experience the awe of excitement through fierce battles, breathtaking cinematics, and intriguing novelties.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902860/extras/2024-09-17_14-27-03.gif?t=1736492231\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>A World Full of Secrets</strong></h2>The world of Light Odyssey is full of secrets left behind by a lost civilization. What happened on this desolate planet? It is up to you to shed light on this mystery by unlocking secrets behind the symbols and writings from the long-forgotten past.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902860/extras/2024-09-17_14-27-28.gif?t=1736492231\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Wide Range of Upgrades</strong></h2>You can unlock new abilities as you battle through the colossi and discover new secrets. Upgrade your abilities and use them for your survival.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902860/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736492231","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902860/page.bg.jpg?t=1